\tan(\theta+hdg)
\tan (90^\circ - w) = \cot w = \frac{1}{\tan w}
w = hdg - \theta
\tan (90^\circ - (hdg - \theta)) = \frac{1}{\tan (hdg-\theta)} = \frac{1}{\frac{\tan hdg - \tan \theta}{1+\tan hdg \tan \theta}} = \frac{1 + \tan hdg \tan \theta}{\tan hdg - \tan \theta}
