\cos(\theta+\delta) = \cos\theta-(\alpha\cos\theta+\beta\sin\theta)
\sin(\theta+\delta) = \sin\theta-(\alpha\sin\theta-\beta\cos\theta)
\alpha=2\sin^2\frac\delta2,\qquad\beta=\sin\delta
